Biomass Briquette.title: Biomass Briquette
Biomass Briquette.subtitle: Eco-friendly, compact fuel blocks from biomass and waste materials
Biomass Briquette.description: Biomass Briquette is an alternative fuel source made from agricultural or industrial byproducts. It ensures high calorific value, low emissions, and is suitable for boilers, furnaces, and domestic heating.
usesdescription: Used in gasifiers and power plants
